data.description:
Amazing 3+ bedrooms/2 bath home. This fine home features eat in kitchen, formal dining with original built-in hutch, beautiful original woodwork and built-ins, pocket doors, open staircase, living room with gas fireplace, 2nd floor den that could also be the 4th bedroom, open staircase and large welcoming foyer!!  
Two nice storage rooms in basement for multi-purpose use or could be made into 2 additional bedrooms. 
Livable attic space.
Sheet rock and electrical are complete and would make an amazing master bedroom! 
Fabulous 30 x 36 heated, insulated garage with alley access.
Maintenance free steel siding. You will love this home! Small town living at its best!!
